ruckusCtrlApRadioStatsRxPkts.name: ruckusCtrlApRadioStatsRxPkts
ruckusCtrlApRadioStatsRxPkts.description: Total received radio packets of this AP radio. This counter is from driver; it contains retry/duplicate values and 802.11 headers, so it's value is bigger than the calculated value from Wlan.

ruckusCtrlApRadioStatsTxPkts.name: ruckusCtrlApRadioStatsTxPkts
ruckusCtrlApRadioStatsTxPkts.description: Total transmitted radio packets of this AP radio.This counter is from driver; it contains retry/duplicate values and 802.11 headers, so it's value is bigger than the calculated value from Wlan.

ruckusCtrlApRadioStatsTxRetryPkts.name: ruckusCtrlApRadioStatsTxRetryPkts
ruckusCtrlApRadioStatsTxRetryPkts.description: How many times the driver asks HW to resend in this AP radio. The HW may have resent several times before informing driver that it fails. This value is calculated at SW side, not the underneath HW one. Each SW send may incur several HW retry.
